        {
            "title": "Apollo總裁為私募信貸辯護,面對散戶贖回潮",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XWsZ8ddPYfILX30PDuf3qw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/75dbe1cc93772c032a4108468fcf1ba1_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Apollo Global Management Inc.總裁Jim Zelter週四為私募信貸辯護,將近期投資者的擔憂描述為\"成長的陣痛\",並稱有關散戶投資者撤資的頭條新聞過度渲染了直接貸款行業\"邊緣的小衝突\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Zelter在接受彭博電視台採訪時表示,贖回上限已明確列明並按預期運作。他指出,基金文件明確規定了5%的贖回結構,旨在保護所有投資者。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2533f790-9d2e-3d7c-a6d7-7089ccb3e1bf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在上週於亞洲舉行的一次會議上,Zelter暗示某些分銷渠道可能未能充分向散戶投資者傳達私募信貸風險,造成短期贖回需求的錯配。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">商業發展公司,即面向散戶投資者的私募信貸基金,面臨越來越多的贖回請求,原因是市場對這個規模達1.8萬億美元市場的貸款做法以及對容易受人工智能顛覆影響的企業的敞口感到擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據一封股東信函,上個月Apollo將其規模達250億美元的Apollo Debt Solutions基金的撤資上限設定為已發行股份的5%,此前客戶尋求贖回11.2%的份額。BlackRock Inc.、Blue Owl Capital Inc.和Ares Management Corp.也對類似基金限制了撤資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些贖回請求引發了關於直接貸款這種非流動性槓桿融資形式是否適合尋求流動性的投資者的疑問。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">關於中東衝突的影響,Zelter表示,當衝突結束時,海灣主權財富基金可能會更加關注國內資本支出,儘管他尚未觀察到任何阻礙其更廣泛投資目標的因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/apollo%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E7%82%BA%E7%A7%81%E5%8B%9F%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E8%BE%AF%E8%AD%B7-%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E6%95%A3%E6%88%B6%E8%B4%96%E5%9B%9E%E6%BD%AE-132454532.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 21:42:35",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
